@page "/Diagrams/Serialization"

@using Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor.Diagrams

@*Hidden:Lines*@
@using ej2_blazor_samples
@{
    SampleBrowser.CurrentSampleName = "Save and Load";
    SampleBrowser.CurrentControlName = "Diagram";
    SampleBrowser.CurrentControlCategory = "Diagram";
    SampleBrowser.CurrentControl = SampleBrowser.Config.Diagram;
    SampleBrowser.ActionDescription = new string[] {
        @" <p>
            This sample visualizes building diagrams interactively and editing the saved diagrams. Symbol Palette is used
        to easily build
        diagrams.

        </p>"
    };
    SampleBrowser.Description = new string[] {
        @"<p>
        This example shows how to drag-and-drop shapes and connectors from symbol palette to build diagrams. You can
        save the diagram
        as text files and edit the pre-saved diagrams. The
        <code>SaveDiagram</code> method can be used to save the diagram as string. The
        <code>LoadDiagram</code> method can be used to load the diagram from a string. In this example, context menu
        and
        undo/redo features are enabled.
        </p>

        <br>"
    };
}
@*End:Hidden*@
<div id='toolbar' style="width:100%;height: 10%;margin-top: 10px;">
</div>

<div class="control-section">
    <link href="https://ej2.syncfusion.com/javascript/demos/src/diagram/styles/diagram-common.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <div class="sb-mobile-palette-bar">
        <div id="palette-icon" style="float: right;" role="button" class="e-ddb-icons1 e-toggle-palette"></div>
    </div>
    <div id="palette-space" class="sb-mobile-palette">
        <EjsSymbolPalette id="palettes" Width="100%" Height="700px" SymbolHeight="60" SymbolWidth="60">
            <SymbolMargin Left="15" Right="15" Bottom="15" Top="15"></SymbolMargin>
            <SymbolPalettePalettes>
                <SymbolPalettePalette Id="flow" Expanded="true" Symbols="@flowShapes" IconCss="e-ddb-icons e-flow" Title="Flow Shapes">
                </SymbolPalettePalette>
                <SymbolPalettePalette Id="connectors" Expanded="true" Symbols="@connectors" IconCss="e-ddb-icons e-connector" Title="Connectors">
                </SymbolPalettePalette>
            </SymbolPalettePalettes>
        </EjsSymbolPalette>
    </div>
    <div id="diagram-space" class="sb-mobile-diagram">
        <EjsDiagram Width="100%" Height="690px">
            <DiagramSnapSettings>
                <HorizontalGridlines LineColor="#e0e0e0 " LineIntervals="@lineIntervals">
                </HorizontalGridlines>
                <VerticalGridlines LineColor="#e0e0e0" LineIntervals="@lineIntervals">
                </VerticalGridlines>
            </DiagramSnapSettings>
            <DiagramNodes>
                <DiagramNode Id="Start" Height="50" Width="100" OffsetX="250" OffsetY="60">
                    <DiagramFlowShape Shape="@FlowShapes.Terminator" Type="@Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor.Diagrams.Shapes.Flow"></DiagramFlowShape>
                    <NodeShapeStyle Fill="#d0f0f1" StrokeColor="#797979"></NodeShapeStyle>
                    <DiagramNodeAnnotations>
                        <DiagramNodeAnnotation Content="Start">
                        </DiagramNodeAnnotation>
                    </DiagramNodeAnnotations>
                </DiagramNode>
                <DiagramNode Id="Alarm" Height="50" Width="100" OffsetX="250" OffsetY="160">
                    <DiagramFlowShape Shape="@FlowShapes.Process" Type="@Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor.Diagrams.Shapes.Flow"></DiagramFlowShape>
                    <NodeShapeStyle Fill="#fbfdc5" StrokeColor="#797979"></NodeShapeStyle>
                    <DiagramNodeAnnotations>
                        <DiagramNodeAnnotation Content="Alarm Rings">
                        </DiagramNodeAnnotation>
                    </DiagramNodeAnnotations>
                </DiagramNode>
                <DiagramNode Id="Ready" Height="80" Width="100" OffsetX="250" OffsetY="260">
                    <DiagramFlowShape Shape="@FlowShapes.Decision" Type="@Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor.Diagrams.Shapes.Flow"></DiagramFlowShape>
                    <NodeShapeStyle Fill="#c5efaf" StrokeColor="#797979"></NodeShapeStyle>
                    <DiagramNodeAnnotations>
                        <DiagramNodeAnnotation Content="Ready to Get Up?">
                        </DiagramNodeAnnotation>
                    </DiagramNodeAnnotations>
                </DiagramNode>
                <DiagramNode Id="Climb" Height="50" Width="100" OffsetX="250" OffsetY="370">
                    <DiagramFlowShape Shape="@FlowShapes.Process" Type="@Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor.Diagrams.Shapes.Flow"></DiagramFlowShape>
                    <NodeShapeStyle Fill="#fbfdc5" StrokeColor="#797979"></NodeShapeStyle>
                    <DiagramNodeAnnotations>
                        <DiagramNodeAnnotation Content="Climb out of Bed">
                        </DiagramNodeAnnotation>
                    </DiagramNodeAnnotations>
                </DiagramNode>
                <DiagramNode Id="End" Height="50" Width="105" OffsetX="250" OffsetY="460">
                    <DiagramFlowShape Shape="@FlowShapes.Terminator" Type="@Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor.Diagrams.Shapes.Flow"></DiagramFlowShape>
                    <NodeShapeStyle Fill="#d0f0f1" StrokeColor="#797979"></NodeShapeStyle>
                    <DiagramNodeAnnotations>
                        <DiagramNodeAnnotation Content="End">
                        </DiagramNodeAnnotation>
                    </DiagramNodeAnnotations>
                </DiagramNode>
                <DiagramNode Id="Relay" Height="50" Width="100" OffsetX="450" OffsetY="160">
                    <DiagramFlowShape Shape="@FlowShapes.Delay" Type="@Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor.Diagrams.Shapes.Flow"></DiagramFlowShape>
                    <NodeShapeStyle Fill="#f8eee5" StrokeColor="#797979"></NodeShapeStyle>
                    <DiagramNodeAnnotations>
                        <DiagramNodeAnnotation Content="Delay">
                        </DiagramNodeAnnotation>
                    </DiagramNodeAnnotations>
                </DiagramNode>
                <DiagramNode Id="Hit" Height="50" Width="100" OffsetX="450" OffsetY="260">
                    <DiagramFlowShape Shape="@FlowShapes.Process" Type="@Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor.Diagrams.Shapes.Flow"></DiagramFlowShape>
                    <NodeShapeStyle Fill="#fbfdc5" StrokeColor="#797979"></NodeShapeStyle>
                    <DiagramNodeAnnotations>
                        <DiagramNodeAnnotation Content="Hit Snooze button">
                        </DiagramNodeAnnotation>
                    </DiagramNodeAnnotations>
                </DiagramNode>
            </DiagramNodes>
            <DiagramConnectors>
                <DiagramConnector Id="connector1" SourceID="Start" TargetID="Alarm">
                    <ConnectorShapeStyle StrokeColor="#797979"></ConnectorShapeStyle>
                    <ConnectorTargetDecorator Shape="@DecoratorShapes.Arrow" Height="5" Width="5">
                        <DecoratorShapeStyle StrokeColor="#797979" Fill="#797979"></DecoratorShapeStyle>
                    </ConnectorTargetDecorator>
                </DiagramConnector>
                <DiagramConnector Id="connector2" SourceID="Alarm" TargetID="Ready">
                    <ConnectorShapeStyle StrokeColor="#797979"></ConnectorShapeStyle>
                    <ConnectorTargetDecorator Shape="@DecoratorShapes.Arrow" Height="5" Width="5">
                        <DecoratorShapeStyle StrokeColor="#797979" Fill="#797979"></DecoratorShapeStyle>
                    </ConnectorTargetDecorator>
                </DiagramConnector>
                <DiagramConnector Id="connector3" SourceID="Ready" TargetID="Climb">
                    <ConnectorShapeStyle StrokeColor="#797979"></ConnectorShapeStyle>
                    <ConnectorTargetDecorator Shape="@DecoratorShapes.Arrow" Height="5" Width="5">
                        <DecoratorShapeStyle StrokeColor="#797979" Fill="#797979"></DecoratorShapeStyle>
                    </ConnectorTargetDecorator>
                </DiagramConnector>
                <DiagramConnectorAnnotations>
                    <DiagramConnectorAnnotation Content="Yes">
                        <ConnectorAnnotationStyle Fill="white"></ConnectorAnnotationStyle>
                    </DiagramConnectorAnnotation>
                </DiagramConnectorAnnotations>
                <DiagramConnector Id="connector4" SourceID="Climb" TargetID="End">
                    <ConnectorShapeStyle StrokeColor="#797979"></ConnectorShapeStyle>
                    <ConnectorTargetDecorator Shape="@DecoratorShapes.Arrow" Height="5" Width="5">
                        <DecoratorShapeStyle StrokeColor="#797979" Fill="#797979"></DecoratorShapeStyle>
                    </ConnectorTargetDecorator>
                </DiagramConnector>
                <DiagramConnector Id="connector5" SourceID="Ready" TargetID="Hit">
                    <ConnectorShapeStyle StrokeColor="#797979"></ConnectorShapeStyle>
                    <ConnectorTargetDecorator Shape="@DecoratorShapes.Arrow" Height="5" Width="5">
                        <DecoratorShapeStyle StrokeColor="#797979" Fill="#797979"></DecoratorShapeStyle>
                    </ConnectorTargetDecorator>
                    <DiagramConnectorAnnotations>
                        <DiagramConnectorAnnotation Content="Yes">
                            <ConnectorAnnotationStyle Fill="white"></ConnectorAnnotationStyle>
                        </DiagramConnectorAnnotation>
                    </DiagramConnectorAnnotations>
                </DiagramConnector>
                <DiagramConnector Id="connector6" SourceID="Hit" TargetID="Relay">
                    <ConnectorShapeStyle StrokeColor="#797979"></ConnectorShapeStyle>
                    <ConnectorTargetDecorator Shape="@DecoratorShapes.Arrow" Height="5" Width="5">
                        <DecoratorShapeStyle StrokeColor="#797979" Fill="#797979"></DecoratorShapeStyle>
                    </ConnectorTargetDecorator>
                </DiagramConnector>
                <DiagramConnector Id="connector7" SourceID="Relay" TargetID="Alarm">
                    <ConnectorShapeStyle StrokeColor="#797979"></ConnectorShapeStyle>
                    <ConnectorTargetDecorator Shape="@DecoratorShapes.Arrow" Height="5" Width="5">
                        <DecoratorShapeStyle StrokeColor="#797979" Fill="#797979"></DecoratorShapeStyle>
                    </ConnectorTargetDecorator>
                </DiagramConnector>
            </DiagramConnectors>
        </EjsDiagram>
    </div>
</div>
